701420f-a.title: Bronx: Magenta Street - Barker Avenue
701420f-a.text:
Magenta Street (left), south side, east from Barker to
Olinville Avenes. The long building, in the background, is
Public School No. 41, at the S.E. corner of Olinville Avenue.
June 16, 1938.
P. L. Snerr
NO REPRODUCTIOIIS.

701422f-a.title: Bronx: Magenta Street - Barker Avenue
701422f-a.text:
Magenta Street, north side, east from Barker Avenue to White
Flains Road. On the latter appears part of the elevated structure
of the I.R.T. subway.
June 16, 1938
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
